{"Id":451823,"Title":"劫灰","Dynasty":"近现代","Author":"添雪斋","Context":"石炭纪，二叠纪。三叠纪，侏罗纪。白垩纪，第三纪。或裸子，或被子。亿载生，亿载死。涅为石，凝筋髓。储阳和，融金水。育电阙，驱钢兕。逢瑞世，价倍蓰。掘千寻，探其址。火井间，烷气里。发万氓，求一匦。得一匦，血累累。黑玉色，践酣紫。氓者殇，如敝屣。氓者生，如蝼蚁。斯人去，须防弭。国有器，难怙恃。国克谐，请誉美。仅戋馀，某篇诔。百十字，载片纸。槐花开，瑩白蕊。槐花落，雪浩弥。石有心，涕泗起：“吾魂黑，曰谥燬。名劫灰，劫未止。阳和变，杀气始。夭砂丁，实上旨。匪吾非，匪吾是。谓何哉，谓天只”。复春深，耘春耔。田畻间，彼妇仔。日继日，望而跂。土半抔，归家矣。远天霁，云流绮。采采之，青芣苢。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":4,"Rank":1500,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"78c90fed27c6fbef9f439b2a455336ce","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":4855204,"Sentence":"槐花开，瑩白蕊。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"huái huā kāi ，yīng bái rui ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":21,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4855183,"Sentence":"石炭纪，二叠纪。","Rank":500,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"dàn tàn ji ，èr dié ji ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4855184,"Sentence":"三叠纪，侏罗纪。","Rank":1000,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"sān dié ji ，zhū luó ji ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4855185,"Sentence":"白垩纪，第三纪。","Rank":200,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"bái è ji ，dì sān ji ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4855186,"Sentence":"或裸子，或被子。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"huò luǒ zi ，huò bèi zi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4855187,"Sentence":"亿载生，亿载死。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yì zǎi shēng ，yì zǎi si ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4855188,"Sentence":"涅为石，凝筋髓。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"niè wéi dàn ，nǐng jīn sui ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4855189,"Sentence":"储阳和，融金水。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"chǔ yáng hé ，róng jīn shui ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4855190,"Sentence":"育电阙，驱钢兕。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yō diàn quē ，qū gāng sì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"Engl